01:00:43.504 --> 01:00:48.985
MATT: What darkvision is, it's very black and
white. You don't see a lot of color, and it's hard

01:00:48.985 --> 01:00:52.407
at this distance to make out anything. Without
feeling it or seeing it, it's hard to get

01:00:52.407 --> 01:00:53.425
details.

01:00:53.425 --> 01:00:56.089
LIAM: I checked the door, but I didn't check
anything else. Can I check the room for traps?

01:00:56.089 --> 01:00:57.242
MATT: Yeah, if you'd like to.

01:00:57.242 --> 01:01:01.063
LIAM: I would like to. Rolled a 23.

