SAM: Not the face!

01:31:02.673 --> 01:31:06.677
MATT: But you strike down and you find it hit the
gem and then slide off as it hits, but you feel it

01:31:06.677 --> 01:31:09.919
give a bit on the impact. Anyone else want to do
