TALIESIN: Whitestone's pretty strong.

01:32:00.408 --> 01:32:04.421
SAM: Can't it burn? Can't you do things with
stone, Keyleth?

01:32:04.421 --> 01:32:10.358
TRAVIS: You have lightning. Are we going to kill
ourselves if we do that?

01:32:10.358 --> 01:32:15.800
TALIESIN: You could stone, you could get out of
this.

01:32:15.800 --> 01:32:17.367
MATT: So what's the damage on that?

01:32:17.367 --> 01:32:18.805
LAURA: I know.

01:32:18.805 --> 01:32:24.557
MARISHA: I couldn't take Move Earth because we
needed Sunbeam. I have Wall of Stone.

01:32:24.557 --> 01:32:26.029
SAM: What does that do?

01:32:26.029 --> 01:32:27.657
TRAVIS: It could buy us more time if we get on
it.

01:32:27.657 --> 01:32:28.865
LAURA: 43.

01:32:28.865 --> 01:32:37.106
MATT: 43? It hits the glass and as the explosion
settles the smoke rises up and you can see a

01:32:37.106 --> 01:32:42.727
portion of the glass wall about ten feet up,
shards have been chiseled out from the explosion.

01:32:42.727 --> 01:32:46.980
It's taken some damage. Not a heavy amount, but
you can see there has been a portion of the wall

01:32:46.980 --> 01:32:49.375
that has been scraped away.

01:32:49.375 --> 01:32:50.560
TRAVIS: About ten feet up?

01:32:50.560 --> 01:32:51.629
MATT: About ten feet up.

01:32:51.629 --> 01:32:52.521
LAURA: Grog!

01:32:52.521 --> 01:32:54.598
TRAVIS: Can I run over there? I'd have to run
through the acid?

01:32:54.598 --> 01:33:00.552
MATT: You would have to, yeah, unless you want to
try and jump across. You could try and jump across

01:33:00.552 --> 01:33:01.539
if you want to.

01:33:01.539 --> 01:33:07.566
TRAVIS: Yes, I would like to jump across, run
over, and start swinging on that section.

01:33:07.566 --> 01:33:08.425
MATT: Okay.

01:33:08.425 --> 01:33:09.775
SAM: What side is this? On the ceiling?

01:33:09.775 --> 01:33:11.892
LAURA: This is on the side that they left
through.

01:33:11.892 --> 01:33:12.942
SAM: Okay.

01:33:12.942 --> 01:33:15.365
MATT: Which, the door is now closed, by the way,
and Vax is nowhere in sight.

01:33:15.365 --> 01:33:16.720
LAURA: The door closed again?

01:33:16.720 --> 01:33:19.991
TRAVIS: Can I do great weapon master and hit it
three times?

01:33:19.991 --> 01:33:22.792
MATT: Yeah.

01:33:22.792 --> 01:33:23.809
TRAVIS: Yeah?

01:33:23.809 --> 01:33:27.498
MATT: Scanlan? Are you making another strike at
the gem?

01:33:27.498 --> 01:33:28.793
SAM: Absolutely, is it my turn again?

01:33:28.793 --> 01:33:31.912
MATT: This is all fluid. We'll pull it up as you
go, and you're taking your shot.

01:33:31.912 --> 01:33:35.821
TALIESIN: I'm taking three shots at one of the
gems on the wall.

01:33:35.821 --> 01:33:36.906
MATT: Okay, go for it.

01:33:36.906 --> 01:33:37.953
SAM: 17 to hit.

01:33:37.953 --> 01:33:39.232
MATT: Hits, go ahead and roll damage.

01:33:39.232 --> 01:33:40.274
SAM: Ten.

01:33:40.274 --> 01:33:44.937
MATT: Ten. You strike down a second time, the acid
now beginning to rise; the level's almost up to

01:33:44.937 --> 01:33:50.280
your chest, and it's a little harder for you to
swing, but you still manage to strike true. You

01:33:50.280 --> 01:33:54.455
