SAM: No. I can take Pike.

01:38:44.264 --> 01:38:45.100
LAURA: Take Pike.

01:38:45.100 --> 01:38:46.526
MATT: You can take one person.

01:38:46.526 --> 01:38:47.722
SAM: Of my height.

01:38:47.722 --> 01:38:49.289
MATT: Of your size. Medium creatures.

01:38:49.289 --> 01:38:52.562
SAM: Oh, my size, not my height?

01:38:52.562 --> 01:38:55.081
MATT: Well, you are, as a gnome, a small creature,
