01:38:55.081 --> 01:38:57.227
LAURA: But he's Percy-sized right now.

01:38:57.227 --> 01:38:58.261
MATT: Pretty sure.

01:38:58.261 --> 01:38:59.706
TALIESIN: Well, it's fake, though.

01:38:59.706 --> 01:39:01.243
LAURA: Oh, right.

