MATT: Let me double-check this real fast. Yeah, a
gnome's considered small, so it would have to be a

01:39:05.203 --> 01:39:06.202
small creature, for you.

01:39:06.202 --> 01:39:07.445
SAM: I can take Pike.

01:39:07.445 --> 01:39:08.603
ASHLEY: All right, let's go.

01:39:08.603 --> 01:39:09.992
LAURA: Do it!

