01:40:06.161 --> 01:40:11.238
right now the acid has lifted to the point where
the next round, everyone's going to start being

01:40:11.238 --> 01:40:13.270
submerged.

01:40:13.270 --> 01:40:21.581
SAM: I take Pike by the hands and I will Dimension
Door out through the glass to where she put her

01:40:21.581 --> 01:40:23.656
hand on the hidden gem. Is that right?

01:40:23.656 --> 01:40:29.450
MATT: Okay. You step out of the acid. It's
dripping off the lower half of your body. This

01:40:29.450 --> 01:40:31.987
sizzling smoke is pouring off your body.

01:40:31.987 --> 01:40:35.395
SAM: My leather pants are singed!

01:40:35.466 --> 01:40:36.791
(laughter)

01:40:36.791 --> 01:40:44.661
MATT: Don't Lenny Kravitz this. You walk up the
ramp, you grab Pike, and the two of you appear on

01:40:44.661 --> 01:40:50.090
the other side of the glass door, up on the
platform where Cassandra pressed the final gem.

01:40:50.090 --> 01:40:56.341
SAM: Pike, now's a good time to talk about us,
