01:40:56.341 --> 01:40:58.274
my hand on the gem.

01:40:58.274 --> 01:40:59.978
ASHLEY: Scanlan, not now!

01:40:59.978 --> 01:41:01.196
SAM: Okay!

01:41:01.196 --> 01:41:06.716
MATT: You put your hand on the gem, and put your
hand away for a second and see the gem itself is

01:41:06.716 --> 01:41:10.260
glowing, but does not seem to be--

01:41:10.332 --> 01:41:14.836
SAM: Try to put your hands on the other
non-destroyed gems!

01:41:14.918 --> 01:41:17.176
MATT: Make another strength check now, with the
Heat Metal.

01:41:17.176 --> 01:41:18.542
LAURA: Okay.

01:41:18.542 --> 01:41:20.124
TRAVIS: I'm running over to the other gems.

01:41:20.124 --> 01:41:21.611
MARISHA: Come on, Vex.

01:41:21.611 --> 01:41:23.849
LAURA: That's way better! 13?

01:41:23.849 --> 01:41:28.533
MATT: 13? Okay, with the help of the Heat Metal,
which managed to make the metal more pliable, you

01:41:28.533 --> 01:41:33.032
do still take three points of fire damage because
