01:41:59.241 --> 01:42:00.259
SAM: Do that more.

01:42:00.259 --> 01:42:01.666
LAURA: I keep doing it.

01:42:01.666 --> 01:42:05.933
MARISHA: I'm going to switch my Heat Metal spell
over to the other spigot.

01:42:05.933 --> 01:42:09.224
LAURA: And I fly over to the other side and do the
