could either keep directing this one, because

01:42:16.094 --> 01:42:17.971
right now it's just starting to hit the ceiling.

01:42:17.971 --> 01:42:19.174
LAURA: I'll keep directing it.

01:42:19.174 --> 01:42:21.834
MATT: Okay. Moving it over there. What are you
doing?

01:42:21.834 --> 01:42:23.530
TRAVIS: I'm running over to the gem.

01:42:23.530 --> 01:42:25.093
SAM: Put your hands on the gems!

01:42:25.093 --> 01:42:26.466
TALIESIN: I'm running over to a gem.

01:42:26.466 --> 01:42:28.490
MATT: Okay. You guys make your attacks on separate
gems.

01:42:28.490 --> 01:42:31.000
TRAVIS: No, we're going to put our hands on the
