MATT: Okay. So, as you release your hand and the
smoke builds up at your fingertips and then shoots

02:30:40.200 --> 02:30:47.695
off and clings itself to her form, she looks down
with a bit of a grin, half-laughs to herself as

02:30:47.695 --> 02:30:53.078
the smoke bomb gets lobbed. She begins moving her
hands like that to begin casting a spell.

02:30:53.078 --> 02:30:57.838
LAURA: I let go of my arrow and cast Conjure
Barrage with a holy arrow at them.

02:30:57.838 --> 02:30:59.968
MATT: With a holy arrow at them. All righty.

02:30:59.968 --> 02:31:06.610
MARISHA: And I'm going to, if I can peek around
the corner, start lighting up Sunbeam. They're in

02:31:06.610 --> 02:31:09.735
a nice, pretty line, and I like it. It's hot.

02:31:09.735 --> 02:31:12.419
(laughter)

02:31:12.419 --> 02:31:15.731
MATT: It will take you a moment to get over to
that point because you guys are just coming around

02:31:15.731 --> 02:31:28.155
the corner. So, first things first. Percy, you lob
the smoke bomb. (thud, hiss) This area here fills

02:31:28.155 --> 02:31:29.714
with a billowing smoke.

02:31:29.714 --> 02:31:32.009
TALIESIN: I was shooting it right in front of
them.

