04:15:15.438 --> 04:15:16.592
SAM: Damn it.

04:15:16.592 --> 04:15:18.119
LAURA: 11.

04:15:18.119 --> 04:15:19.977
MATT: Nope.

04:15:19.977 --> 04:15:22.703
LAURA: Wait, 13.

04:15:22.703 --> 04:15:25.967
MATT: 13, no. All right, so--

04:15:25.967 --> 04:15:29.732
SAM: This is it. This is it.

04:15:29.732 --> 04:15:44.149
MARISHA: No.

04:15:44.219 --> 04:15:48.970
MATT: 45 plus 30. 75 points of necrotic damage.

04:15:49.039 --> 04:15:51.902
MARISHA: But you were at 76?

04:15:51.902 --> 04:15:58.583
TALIESIN, MARISHA, and SAM: Oh my god.

04:15:58.583 --> 04:16:06.021
MATT: All righty. You're at one hit point. As your
life force is suddenly sucked out of your body and

04:16:06.110 --> 04:16:12.035
you manage to capture what essence of your
existence still holds you aloft. Drifting forward,

04:16:12.035 --> 04:16:14.994
almost toppling over in your Fly spell.

04:16:14.994 --> 04:16:24.672
