04:16:39.995 --> 04:16:41.778
LAURA: Am I close to it?

04:16:41.778 --> 04:16:51.466
MATT: You've moved up to this point. Now you're
right at the edge. The orb suddenly shrinks in a

04:16:51.466 --> 04:16:59.835
flash of an instant, becoming this tiny speck,
this little dark speck in the air, roughly the

04:16:59.835 --> 04:17:16.324
