You, floating through the air? Your flight ends.

04:17:37.402 --> 04:17:39.811
You immediately plummet.

04:17:39.811 --> 04:17:43.209
MARISHA: Can I cast Hold Person? On her?

04:17:43.209 --> 04:17:44.724
SAM: On her?

04:17:44.724 --> 04:17:45.771
MARISHA: Yes!

04:17:45.771 --> 04:17:47.534
MATT: If you want to. It's just going to paralyze
her.

04:17:47.534 --> 04:17:49.046
MARISHA: Oh, I can't hold her?

04:17:49.046 --> 04:18:00.380
MATT: No. So at that height, it's 40 feet. You
fall. You take 3d6 points of damage.

04:18:00.380 --> 04:18:05.188
LAURA: Can I roll for acrobatics? Maybe I can
catch myself.

04:18:05.188 --> 04:18:09.258
MATT: You know what? Roll acrobatics with
disadvantage.

04:18:09.258 --> 04:18:14.104
LAURA: Okay. I don't know where a d20 is.

04:18:14.104 --> 04:18:21.138
LIAM: 20, and? Six.

04:18:21.138 --> 04:18:24.797
LAURA: Acrobatics?

