04:18:28.151 --> 04:18:34.392
MATT: You take four points of fall damage. As you
slam down into the center of this.

04:18:34.392 --> 04:18:36.475
LAURA: And I'm unconscious.

04:18:36.475 --> 04:18:38.560
MATT: You're unconscious on the ground. (thud)

04:18:38.560 --> 04:18:41.451
LAURA: That's my first time I've ever been
unconscious.

04:18:41.451 --> 04:18:42.980
MARISHA: I thought you were going to die.

04:18:42.980 --> 04:18:45.015
TALIESIN: She's still connected to her rope,
though, isn't she?

04:18:45.015 --> 04:18:49.733
LAURA: No. I took out a fancy robe. I was going to
trap the globe.

04:18:49.733 --> 04:18:50.987
LIAM: Whose turn is it?

04:18:50.987 --> 04:18:53.452
ASHLEY: Can I get to her?

04:18:53.452 --> 04:18:56.691
MATT: You guys are up on this roof right now.

04:18:56.691 --> 04:19:00.379
LIAM: I'm leaping. If you let me leap, I'm going
to leap and take an acrobatics check.

04:19:00.379 --> 04:19:02.021
MATT: Acrobatics check, go for it.

04:19:02.021 --> 04:19:06.279
LIAM: 20. Natural fucking 20!

04:19:06.279 --> 04:19:07.483
MATT: Landing on your feet.

04:19:07.483 --> 04:19:08.728
TALIESIN: Parkour!

04:19:08.728 --> 04:19:11.860
LIAM: I have a potion with my sister's name
written on it, and it's going in her mouth.

04:19:11.860 --> 04:19:14.957
MATT: That's as far as you get on your movement,
right there.

04:19:14.957 --> 04:19:16.277
LIAM: All right.

04:19:16.277 --> 04:19:19.998
LAURA: All right. You can kill her!

04:19:19.998 --> 04:19:21.638
MATT: So you rush up.

04:19:21.638 --> 04:19:22.591
LIAM: I'm right there?

04:19:22.591 --> 04:19:25.386
MATT: That's your full movement to get to her. You
can't do anything else.

04:19:25.386 --> 04:19:27.477
LIAM: So I can't do anything else? I can't do a
bonus action? I can't do nothing.

04:19:27.477 --> 04:19:31.325
MATT: Well, you can do a bonus action, but it's an
action to feed a potion to somebody else.

04:19:31.325 --> 04:19:36.102
LIAM: Then I'm throwing a knife at Lady Briarwood,
which I can use a bonus action to attack her.

04:19:36.102 --> 04:19:39.547
MATT: On the ground, you can't see her. She's 40
feet up on the platform. She's completely out of

04:19:39.547 --> 04:19:45.600
your visual sight. You're down inside this hand
groove that's dug in the ground.

04:19:45.600 --> 04:19:47.939
LIAM: Fuck. All right, I'll hold.

04:19:47.939 --> 04:19:50.183
MATT: Who's up next? Who wants to go next?

04:19:50.183 --> 04:19:51.869
MARISHA: Pike!

04:19:51.869 --> 04:19:53.379
ASHLEY: Can I get to her?

04:19:53.379 --> 04:19:57.654
MATT: You're on top of the roof. You're going to
have to leap down to get to her. You're too far

04:19:57.654 --> 04:19:58.519
away.

04:19:58.519 --> 04:19:59.916
LIAM: She's got time.

04:19:59.916 --> 04:20:02.658
MATT: Actually, you could try a spell if you want
to.

04:20:02.658 --> 04:20:04.167
ASHLEY: Say again?

04:20:04.167 --> 04:20:08.738
MATT: You can try a spell if you want to. She's
about 50 feet from you, at an angle.

04:20:08.738 --> 04:20:15.247
ASHLEY: Okay. I'll do a Healing Word.

04:20:15.247 --> 04:20:26.433
MATT: Okay. As you pull up your holy symbol and
begin casting the spell, the divine energy seems

04:20:26.433 --> 04:20:30.739
