effect.

04:20:30.739 --> 04:20:32.871
SAM: So magic doesn't work?

04:20:32.871 --> 04:20:35.694
MARISHA: Is it because we're in this fucking
room?

04:20:35.694 --> 04:20:40.086
MATT: Do you want to stay where you are?

04:20:40.086 --> 04:20:44.652
LIAM: Come on down. Let's party.

04:20:44.652 --> 04:20:46.790
TRAVIS: I'll go next.

04:20:46.790 --> 04:20:53.839
MATT: Grog, you've gotten up now, with the rope,
to the top. Anybody else want to go?

04:20:53.839 --> 04:20:56.210
TALIESIN: I'll take a shot at Lady Briarwood,
since I'm up here.

04:20:56.210 --> 04:20:59.919
MATT: Go for it. And you aren't forgetting your Hex
damage on her, right?

04:20:59.919 --> 04:21:07.759
TALIESIN: I was. I forgot it on the last one. I
remembered that I forgot it. That's 24 to hit.

04:21:07.759 --> 04:21:09.756
MATT: That hits.

04:21:09.756 --> 04:21:19.636
TALIESIN: 13, 14, 15, 16-- 22 points of damage.

04:21:19.636 --> 04:21:22.190
MATT: How do you want to do this?

04:21:22.190 --> 04:21:24.352
SAM: You get to kill Lady Briarwood?

04:21:24.352 --> 04:21:27.556
LAURA: Do it with as little blood as possible. I'm
dead.

04:21:27.556 --> 04:21:29.670
MATT: You're unconscious.

04:21:29.670 --> 04:21:31.454
LAURA: I'm unconscious.

04:21:31.454 --> 04:21:33.830
TRAVIS: I think, if you kill her--

04:21:33.830 --> 04:21:36.644
TALIESIN: It's a little late.

04:21:36.644 --> 04:21:38.288
TRAVIS: Here comes Godzilla.

04:21:38.288 --> 04:21:45.639
MATT: The smoke billowing from your body, the
essence of this creature whispering in your ear,

04:21:45.639 --> 04:21:59.063
