left arm, you said?

04:22:41.794 --> 04:22:42.916
TALIESIN: Right arm.

04:22:42.916 --> 04:22:48.830
MATT: Right arm. (gun blast) Blasts open, the bone
exposed. The arm spins off and clatters to the

04:22:48.830 --> 04:22:57.794
