04:23:07.623 --> 04:23:12.273
TRAVIS: We don't know if she's unconscious or
dead?

04:23:12.273 --> 04:23:13.374
MATT: You don't know.

04:23:13.374 --> 04:23:14.845
LIAM: I'm going to circle around to her right
