TRAVIS: Can I jump down, then?

04:23:21.329 --> 04:23:23.608
LIAM: I'm feeding a potion to my sister.

04:23:23.608 --> 04:23:24.783
MATT: Acrobatics check?

04:23:24.783 --> 04:23:27.663
LIAM: Thank you.

04:23:27.663 --> 04:23:29.816
TRAVIS: 18.

