04:25:30.365 --> 04:25:32.933
TRAVIS: I'll pick her up and start running towards
the door at the back of the room.

04:25:32.933 --> 04:25:34.820
MARISHA: What door is open?

04:25:34.820 --> 04:25:36.018
MATT: Neither.

04:25:36.018 --> 04:25:37.858
LIAM: We've got to get her up and out.

04:25:37.858 --> 04:25:41.567
TRAVIS: What do the doors look like?

04:25:41.567 --> 04:25:45.275
MATT: You can't tell from here. You're too far,
