TALIESIN: I grab it.

04:25:56.228 --> 04:26:00.076
MATT: It takes a couple of tries, but you manage
to get to the 40-foot top there. Make another

04:26:00.076 --> 04:26:01.294
death saving throw.

04:26:01.294 --> 04:26:04.374
LIAM: I'm tying it to my sister right now. Come
on.

04:26:04.374 --> 04:26:05.412
LAURA: Oh no.

04:26:05.412 --> 04:26:11.392
LIAM: Fail. I've tied it around my sister. Pike,
