04:26:29.743 --> 04:26:30.858
TALIESIN and MARISHA: Yes.

04:26:30.858 --> 04:26:33.705
MATT: 17 points of damage from the fall.

04:26:33.705 --> 04:26:34.614
MARISHA: How many?

04:26:34.614 --> 04:26:35.583
MATT: 17 points.

04:26:35.583 --> 04:26:36.831
TALIESIN: Done.

04:26:36.831 --> 04:26:39.469
TRAVIS: I'll run to the door that's closest to
us.

04:26:39.469 --> 04:26:43.268
MATT: You manage to get her up to the top. Grog,
