04:27:12.905 --> 04:27:14.692
Nothing's happening.

04:27:14.692 --> 04:27:16.166
(cursing)

04:27:16.166 --> 04:27:17.510
LIAM: Pull her out of here!

04:27:17.510 --> 04:27:18.817
MATT: Make another death saving throw.

04:27:18.817 --> 04:27:21.035
LAURA: (laughing) Oh my god, I'm going to die.

04:27:21.035 --> 04:27:22.193
MARISHA: You're not going to die.

