LIAM: 12. Save.

04:27:23.507 --> 04:27:24.482
MARISHA: You're saved!

04:27:24.482 --> 04:27:25.679
LIAM: Pull her out!

04:27:25.679 --> 04:27:26.626
LAURA: Oh god!

04:27:26.626 --> 04:27:27.788
MATT: What are you guys doing?

04:27:27.788 --> 04:27:28.836
SAM: Where is she?

04:27:28.836 --> 04:27:32.698
MATT: She's on top of the wall here. She's been
lifted out by Grog and Percival.

04:27:32.698 --> 04:27:35.051
LIAM: I'm running at the wall and I'm trying to
climb it, stupidly.

